An alternative solution could be overriding the `PreSubclassWindow` function of your button&#39;s derived class and posting a user-defined message to the parent window.

**Button class:**

    #define CUSTOM_CREATE_NOTIFY WM_USER+1001 // (add to header file)

	void CCustomButton::PreSubclassWindow()
	{	
